data.description: Wonderful opportunity to own a ranch home in the Laurel Creek subdivision.  This home has been wonderfully maintained and offers an open floor plan with a 2 car garage.  There is a vaulted ceiling and fireplace in the great room.  The kitchen has light cabinets, neutral countertops and pantry.  The Trane HVAC system is only 5 years old.  The primary suite offers a trey ceiling with walk in closet.  The back yard is very private and has a 6 foot privacy fence. Two inch blinds throughout.  Must see!
